overview:
Beautiful and Unspoilt Islands The waters around the Andaman Islands are the Jewel in India·s crown. Having previously been subjected to government access restrictions, these beautiful and unspoilt islands and their pure waters are now open for you to marvel. Divers will be amazed at the abundance and variety of marine life and undamaged coral reefs.

We are based at beach No.1 on Havelock Island and specialise in Dive trips to the best locations in the Andamans
